                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Squiers</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-06-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 16, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Squiers reports that the Cuban authorities decline to allow Chinese to land,
                    claiming that the Chinese minister at Washington was notified on May 15 of the
                    prohibition.) * * *</p>
            </div>
